text(band=header alignment="2" text="De Especie"border="0" color="0" x="672" y="4" height="64" width="306"  name=de_especie_t  font.face="Arial" font.height="-10" font.weight="400"  font.family="2" font.pitch="2" font.charset="0" background.mode="1" background.color="536870912" )
